<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="p.paris;;51" evaluate="all">PPar51</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Π<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ολεμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αῖος</supplied> Δαμοξέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">νωι χαίρειν.</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="22">κβ</num> Τῦβ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied> <num value="12">ιβ</num> εἰς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ὴν <num value="13">ιγ</num> ᾤμη<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν με ἐν Μέμφει</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>βαδίζειν</corr><sic>βατιζειν</sic></choice> με ἀπὸ <choice><corr>λιβὸς</corr><sic>λειβος</sic></choice> ἕως ἀ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">πηλ</supplied>ιώτου 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ ἀναπίπτομαι ἐπ᾽ ἄχυρον κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αὶ ἄν</supplied>θρωπο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀπὸ λιβός μου <choice><corr>ἐ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ρ</supplied>χόμενός</corr><sic>εχομενος</sic></choice> μου <choice><corr>ἀναπίπτει</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline"><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αν</supplied>απιπτι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="unknown" unit="character" desc="vestiges"/></del></subst></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ αὐτὸς καὶ ὥσπερ κεκλειμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ένοι</supplied> μου 

    <lb n="7"/>ἦσαν οἱ ὀφθαλμοί μου καὶ ἐξαί<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">φνης</supplied> <choice><corr>ἀνοίγω</corr><sic>ανυγωι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="8"/>τοὺς ὀφθαλμούς μου καὶ ὁρῶ σοι τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὰς</supplied> διδύμας 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐν τῷ <choice><corr>διδασκαλείῳ</corr><sic>διδασκαληω</sic></choice> τοῦ Τοθῆ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τος</supplied>. ἐκάλεσαν. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἔλεγον· ὅρα μὴ <choice><corr>ὀλιγοψυχῆσθαι</corr><sic>ολιοψυχησθαι</sic></choice>. Τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">οθ</supplied>ῆς <supplied reason="omitted" cert="low">μὴ</supplied> κάμῃ εὕρας 

    <lb n="11"/>τὴν ὁδὸν ἐπ᾽ ἐμέ, ὅτι μεταβέβλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ηκ</supplied>α τὴν κοίτην 

    <lb n="12"/>μου. ἤκουσα Τοθῆς λέγων· ἔρρ᾽ εὐθ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ύ</supplied>, 

    <lb n="13"/>τί ταῦτα λέγεις; ἐγὼ καταστήσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>μαι <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">τὰς</supplied> διδύμας 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐπὶ σέ. ὀρῶ σοι αὐτὸν καθιστῶντα 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτὰς καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>κααγω</sic></choice> ἔμπροσθεν αὐτῶν ἐπορευόμην, 

    <lb n="16"/>ἕως καταλάβω αὐτὰς καὶ ἔρχομαι εἰς τὴν <choice><corr>ῥύμην</corr><sic>ρυβην</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="17"/>μετ᾽ αὐτῶν. ἔλεγον αὐτὰς <sic>αὐτὰς</sic> ὅτι ἔτι βραχὺ 

    <lb n="18"/>ἔχω ἐν τῷ <choice><corr>ἀέρι</corr><sic>αθρει</sic></choice> καὶ πρωὶ <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">  </supplied> ἔσται ὃ ἤμην. <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>ὐθὺ <choice><corr>εἶδον</corr><sic>ιδον</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/>μίαν αὐτῶν ἐρχομένην πρὸς τό τι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>ος εἰς <choice><corr><supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">σ</supplied>κοτινὸν</corr><sic>κοτινον</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="20"/>τόπον καὶ καθιζάνει <choice><corr>οὐροῦσα</corr><sic>ορουσα</sic></choice>. εἶδον εὐθὺ ὅτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied> μίαν αὐτῶν 

    <lb n="21"/>ἀποκεκάθισται. <choice><corr>εἶπον</corr><sic>ειπα</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Ἁρμάει</corr><sic>αρμαεις</sic></choice> π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ι</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/> <choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐ</supplied>λθεῖν</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>λθιν</sic></choice> αὐτόν. 

    <lb n="22"/>καὶ ἄλλα τινὰ εἶδον πολλὰ καὶ πάλιν ἠξίωκα τὸν 

    <lb n="23"/>Σάραπιν καὶ τὴν Ἶσιν λέγων· ἐλθέ μοι θεὰ θεῶν, 

    <lb n="24"/><choice><corr>ἵλεως</corr><sic>ειλεως</sic></choice> γινομένη ἐπάκουσόν μου ἐλέησον τὰς διδύμας, 

    <lb n="25"/>σὺ <choice><corr>κατέδειξας</corr><sic>κατεδιξας</sic></choice> διδύμας. ἐμὲ δὲ ἄφες, <choice><corr>ἰδού</corr><sic>ειδου</sic></choice>, πολιὰς <choice><corr>ἔχοντα</corr><sic>εχων</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="26"/>ἀλλὰ οἶδα ὅτι ἐν <choice><corr>ὀλίγῳ</corr><sic>ολιο</sic></choice> <choice><corr>χρόνῳ</corr><sic>χρωνω</sic></choice> παύσομαι, αὗται δὲ 

    <lb n="27"/>γυναῖκές εἰσιν. ἐὰν μιανθῶσιν, οὐ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>ὴ γένονται 

    <lb n="28"/>καθαραὶ <choice><corr>πώποτε</corr><sic>ποποτε</sic></choice>. τῇ <num value="14">ιδ</num> ᾤμην με ἐν Ἀλεξαν-

    <lb n="29"/>δρήᾳ με εἶναι ἐπάνω πύργου μεγάλου. εἶχον 

    <lb n="30"/><choice><corr>πρόσωπον</corr><sic>προσοπον</sic></choice> καλόν <sic>εἶχον</sic> καὶ οὐκ ἤθελον <choice><corr>οὐθενὶ</corr><sic>ουθενει</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="31"/><choice><corr>δεῖξαί</corr><sic>διξαι</sic></choice> μου τὸ <choice><corr>πρόσωπον</corr><sic>πορσωπον</sic></choice> διὰ τὸ καλὸν αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="32"/>εἶν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ι καὶ <choice><corr>γραῦ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ς</supplied></corr><sic>γραυ</sic></choice> μοι <subst><add place="inline">παρεκάθητο</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">παρε<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del>καθητο</del></subst> καὶ ὄχλος ἀπὸ βορρᾶ μου 

    <lb n="33"/>καὶ ἀπὸ <choice><corr>ἀπηλιώτου</corr><sic>πηλιοτης</sic></choice>. κράζ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ουσι</supplied> <choice><corr>ἠνθρακίσθαι</corr><sic>η<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>θρεκισθαι</sic></choice> ἄνθρωπον 

    <lb n="34"/>πολλαῖς <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">  </supplied> καὶ λέγει μοι· <choice><corr>πρόσμεινον</corr><sic>προσμινον</sic></choice> βραχὺ καὶ ἄξω σε 

    <lb n="35"/>πρὸς τὸν δαίμονα Κνῆφιν, <choice><corr><supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ἵν</supplied>α</corr><sic>α</sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">προ</supplied>σκυνήσῃς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ὐτόν. 

    <lb n="36"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ᾤμην</corr><sic>ομην</sic></choice> με <choice><corr>πρεσβύτῃ</corr><sic>προσβυτη</sic></choice> με λέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γειν</supplied>· <choice><corr>πάτερ</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">π</supplied>ατηρ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear></del></sic></choice>, οὐχ <choice><corr>ὁρᾷς</corr><sic>ωρας</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="37"/>τὸ ὅραμα τοῦτο ὃ <choice><corr>τεθέαμαι</corr><sic>τεθηαμαι</sic></choice>; δι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ηγησά</supplied>μην αὐτῷ. <choice><corr>ἔδωκέ</corr><sic>εδοκε</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="38"/>μοι <choice><corr>δύο</corr><sic>δυω</sic></choice> καλάμους. ἐπιβλέψ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ας τα</supplied>χὺ εἶδον τὸν Κνῆφιν. 

    <lb n="39"/><choice><corr>εὐφραίνεσθε</corr><sic>ευφρανεσθαι</sic></choice>, οἱ παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ πάν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τες· ἄφ</supplied>εσίς μοι γίνεται ταχύ. 

    <lb n="40"/>ἄλλα <choice><corr>τεθέαμαι</corr><sic>τεθηαμαι</sic></choice>. <choice><corr>καλλίω</corr><sic>καλλειο</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ταῦθ᾽</corr><sic>ταυτ</sic></choice> ὅλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ως. οἶ</supplied>δας ὅτι <sic>κεῖταί μοι</sic> 

    <lb n="41"/><choice><corr>πρόκειταί</corr><sic>πρωκειται</sic></choice> μοι <choice><corr>ἀσφαλῆ</corr><sic>ασ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del>φαλην</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἔχ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ειν</supplied></corr><sic>εχ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ιν</supplied></sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ὅρ</supplied>μον τὰς διδύμας. 

    <lb n="42"/>εὐλαβοῦμαι ἄλλ᾽ οὐθέν. ταῦτα ἡ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ώρακ</supplied>α ἕως Φαμενώθ. 

    <lb n="43"/>λοιπὸν παρακάλει τὰς διδύμα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς </supplied><choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐλθ</supplied>εῖν</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ελθ</supplied>ιν</sic></choice> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἔδ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κε</unclear></del> 

    <lb n="44"/><choice><corr>εἰπέ</corr><sic>ιπη</sic></choice> τε ὅτι ἐκπορεύομαι. ὀ Ἀμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῶσις</supplied> ἥκει ἐπ᾽ ἐμέ, 

    <lb n="45"/>ἔδωκέ μοι τὴν ὁδὸν καὶ διέσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τη τὸ </supplied><choice><corr><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">π</supplied>α<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">σ</supplied>τ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ο</supplied>φόριον</corr><sic><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">π</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>τφοριον</sic></choice> ἔμπροσ-

    <lb n="46"/>θέν μου. 

    <lb n="47"/>ε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὐτ</supplied>ύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.3469" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3469" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-0159-02-12">nach 12. Febr. 159 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3469" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Griechisch - demotisch.</p></div><div n="meta.3469" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 2: <date type="mentioned" value="-0159-02-10">10. Febr. 159 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3469" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">78</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">3469</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">78</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0245;1;78" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3469" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">363</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.3469" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">P.Par., Planche XXXV</bibl><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Delekat, Katoche, Abb. 1</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.3469"